{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 75,
  "title": "第七十五章（貴生）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "人之饑也 以亓取食稅之多也 是以飢"
    },
    {
      "text": "百姓之不治也 以亓上有以為也 是以不治"
    },
    {
      "text": "民之輕死 以亓求生之厚也 是以輕死"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫唯无以生為者 是賢貴生"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人民所以饑深者，以其君上稅食下太多，民皆化上為貪，叛道違德，故饑。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "民之不可治者，以其君上多欲，好有為也，",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "是以其民化上有為，情偽難治。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人民所以侵犯死者，以其求生活之道太厚，貪利以自危。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 13,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以求生太厚之故，輕入死地也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫唯獨無以生為務者，爵祿不干於意，財利不入於身，天子不得臣，諸侯不得使，則賢於貴生也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言民之所以僻，治之所以亂，皆由上不由其下也，民從上也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
